### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَلَقَدْ كُنتُمْ تَمَنَّوْنَ ٱلْمَوْتَ مِن قَبْلِ أَن تَلْقَوْهُ فَقَدْ رَأَيْتُمُوهُ وَأَنتُمْ تَنظُرُونَ</span>

### English

You certainly wished ˹for the opportunity˺ for martyrdom before encountering it, now you have seen it with your own eyes.